{
    "componentChunkName": "component---src-templates-smell-article-template-tsx",
    "path": "/what-comment",
    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"what-comment\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#what-comment\" aria-label=\"what comment permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>\"What\" Comment</h2>\n<p>Recognizing all comments as Code Smells is controversial and raises many different opinions. For this reason, I define a concrete subcategory of comments named <em>\"What\" Comments</em> that clearly defines only these comments, which in the vast majority will hint at something smells. The rule is simple: If a comment describes <em>what</em> is happening in a particular code section, it is probably trying to mask some other Code Smell.</p>\n<p>This distinction leaves room for the <em>\"Why\" Comments</em> which were already defined by Wake in 2004 and were considered helpful. Wake also notes that comments that cite non-obvious algorithms are also acceptable [<a href=\"#sources\">1</a>]. I wanted to mention that comments may have their places in a few more cases, such as extreme optimizations, note discussion conclusions for future reference after a code review, or some additional explanations in domain-specific knowledge.</p>\n<p>The problem is that <em>Comments</em> are generally smelly, as I have mentioned. This is because they are a deodorant for other smells [<a href=\"#sources\">2</a>]. They may also quickly degrade with time and become another category of comments <a href=\"/smells/fallacious-comment\">Fallacious Comments</a>, which are a rotten, misleading subcategory of [<em>\"What\" Comments</em>].</p>\n<h3 id=\"causation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#causation\" aria-label=\"causation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Causation</h3>\n<p>The author sees that the code is confusing and tries to be helpful by adding explanations.</p>\n<h3 id=\"problems\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#problems\" aria-label=\"problems permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Problems</h3>\n<h4 id=\"duplication\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#duplication\" aria-label=\"duplication permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Duplication</strong></h4>\n<p>Bad docstrings, which are just duplicating everything that can be understood from the method name and parameter names &#x26; type annotations, are cluttering the code, possibly sooner or later on the first occasion, they might become <a href=\"/smells/fallacious-comment\">Fallacious Comments</a>.</p>\n<h4 id=\"cover-up-for-other-smells\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cover-up-for-other-smells\" aria-label=\"cover up for other smells permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Cover up for other smells</strong></h4>\n<p>A comment that must explain what is happening in the code indicates that it can't speak for itself, which is a strong indicator of present code smells.</p>\n<h3 id=\"examples\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-label=\"examples permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h3>\n<div class=\"example-block\">\n<p><em>\"What\" Comment</em> as a Grouping Label</p>\n<h4 id=\"smelly\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#smelly\" aria-label=\"smelly permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Smelly</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token comment\"># Creating Report</span>\n        vanilla_report <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> get_vanilla_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        tweaked_report <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> tweaking_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>vanilla_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        final_report <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> format_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>tweaked_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token comment\"># Sending Report</span>\n        send_report_to_headquarters_via_email<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>final_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        send_report_to_developers_via_chat<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>final_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"solution\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#solution\" aria-label=\"solution permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Solution</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n        report <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>create_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>send_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>report<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">create_report</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        vanilla_report <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> get_vanilla_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        tweaked_report <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> tweaking_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>vanilla_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> format_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>tweaked_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">send_report</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> report<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        send_report_to_headquarters_via_email<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>final_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        send_report_to_developers_via_chat<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>final_report<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"example-block\">\n<p><em>\"What\" Comment</em> as a cover for <a href=\"/smells/uncommunicative-name\">Uncommunicative Name</a> code smell.</p>\n<h4 id=\"smelly-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#smelly-1\" aria-label=\"smelly 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Smelly</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\">\n<span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">get_gross_value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> t<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token triple-quoted-string string\">\"\"\"\n    params\n     - price: float\n     - tax: float\n    \"\"\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"solution-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#solution-1\" aria-label=\"solution 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Solution</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">get_gross_value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>price<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">float</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> tax<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">float</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"example-block\">\n<p><em>\"What\" Comment</em> as a cover for <a href=\"/smells/uncommunicative-name\">Uncommunicative Name</a> code smell.</p>\n<h4 id=\"smelly-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#smelly-2\" aria-label=\"smelly 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Smelly</h4>\n<p>Example of useless comment as a docstring.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">increase_attack</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token triple-quoted-string string\">\"\"\" Increases attack by the given value.\n\n    params:\n      - value: integer\n    \"\"\"</span>\n    self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>attack <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> value</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"counter-example\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#counter-example\" aria-label=\"counter example permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Counter example</h4>\n<p>Example of more useful comment as a docstring.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">destroy_character</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>character_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token triple-quoted-string string\">\"\"\"\n    Removes the character from the main game world scene\n    if it's present, otherwise throws a warning (character\n    could be removed due to some other trigger event).\n    \"\"\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"solution-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#solution-2\" aria-label=\"solution 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Solution</h4>\n<p>The only counter indication for removing the docstring, would be when poor auto-documentation requirements are enforced.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">increase_attack</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>attack <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> value</code></pre></div>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"refactoring\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#refactoring\" aria-label=\"refactoring permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></pa